data.description: Welcome home to Western Branch!  Bright and airy move-in ready 4 bedroom ranch in Dunedin, boasting an updated open-concept kitchen / living area with bar seating, butcher block counters, stainless steel appliances, and LVP flooring.  Updated bathrooms and fresh paint throughout.  Well-maintained with the roof, windows and HVAC having been replaced over the years (see attached Feature Sheet).  Grab your furniture and move in quickly, then relax on the covered ground-level deck overlooking your spacious backyard.  But get here soon before it's gone!
